        "content": "<p>Hi, what am I doing wrong here?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ToJson</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FromJson</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">toJson</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">fromJson?</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">structure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Timer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">where</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">due</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">deriving</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Repr</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ToJson</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FromJson</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mySerializedTimer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">String</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">toString</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">toJson</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">due</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">123</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Timer</span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mySerializedTimer</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">myDeserializedTimer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Except</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">String</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Timer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">fromJson?</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mySerializedTimer</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- Expected this to parse successfully, but fails with: Except.error \"Timer.id: Natural number expected\"</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">myDeserializedTimer</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
